TAP-Harness-BailOnFail
======================

This module allows tools using Test::Harness to bail after encountering the
first failure.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    TAP::Harness::Restricted
    Test::More

